  ('ca06e011-0e5a-41ed-83bb-7961d96fc321', 'mathematics', '2', 'Number Sense', '1.3', 'Introduction to the Subject :', 'digit numbers will be beneficial to them as they become fluent in their use and as a prerequisite for the higher', '', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00'),
  ('7e2ca444-3520-4c3b-8b2d-e1daa8303164', 'mathematics', '2', 'Number Sense', '1.4', 'Introduction to the subject: Place value is one of the key concepts in mathematics. Place value encompasses not only position and value of digits but', 'digit numbers, and more difficult computation. It is important that children understand that while a digit can be the same, its value depends on where it is in the number.', '', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00'),
  ('78a401fb-ffe5-4a65-bacc-fec420300544', 'mathematics', '2', 'Number Sense', '2.1', 'Introduction to the Subject :', 'for example, cooking and sharing. Learning and understanding fractions provides a building block for other math skills that students will have to learn. Students are expected to di vide shapes into equal parts creating: halves, thirds and quarters. They should also use the fraction’s names correctly while describing them.', '', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00'),
  ('55c7a29a-fa2d-4725-a18b-8d55fd4daf6f', 'mathematics', '2', 'Number Sense', '2.2', 'Introduction to the Subject : Fractions are a central part of our life ; we constantly use fractions in our daily activities without knowing it. There are', 'for example, cooking and sharing. Learning and understanding fractions provides a building block for other math skills that students will have to learn. Students are expected to di vide shapes into equal parts creating: halves, thirds and quarters. They should also use the fractions names correctly while describing them .', '', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00'),
