  ('8e18d7b6-c555-4f1a-bd8e-b416da9abd4c', 'mathematics', '2', 'Operations with Numbers', '1.2', 'Introduction to the Subject :', 'to-day activities. Buying and selling, giving and receiving all requires us to add or subtract. Students must learn these everyday skills to prepare them for their future. Addition and sub traction prepare children to learn other math content which is also pertinent to their daily lives.', '', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00', '2025-12-19T03:09:53.600637+00:00'),
